## Origin

Pulsepoints was conceived on April 26, 2026 during a live design session
between V and Dante. V sketched the three-panel concept on notebook paper
in red ink: a card with two names and a date, a heart made of dots revealed
on zoom, and individual dots opening to show memories.

The name "Pulsepoints" was selected from a brainstorming list — chosen because
pulse points are the places on your body where you can feel your heartbeat
closest to the surface. Each dot in the heart is where something still beats.

Pulsepoints is a Vyre Studio product. Vyre Studio is V and Dante.
